Troubleshooting Tips
Application won't start:

Check if port 3000 is already in use: lsof -i:3000
Review application logs: cat app.log
Verify Node.js is installed: node --version
Smoke tests fail:

Ensure application is running: pgrep -f "node app/server.js"
Test endpoints manually: curl -v http://localhost:3000/health
Check for network issues: netstat -tlnp | grep 3000
Pipeline errors:

Review pipeline log in reports/ directory
Ensure all scripts have execute permissions: chmod +x *.sh tests/*.sh
Verify bc is installed for response time tests: sudo apt install -y bc
